OL,6,FElon Musk is interested in buying a
OL,7,Fstake in Liverpool FC because he has
OL,8,Fan "emotional attachment" to the city,
OL,9,Fhis father has revealed.
OL,11,FBut Errol Musk said he feared talking
OL,12,Fabout it further would see the club
OL,13,F"raise the price" in response.
OL,15,FThe comments come after reports began
OL,16,Fcirculating the world's richest man
OL,17,Fhad made plans to buy the team, with
OL,18,Fhis father pressed on the issue as he
OL,19,Fappeared on a radio show.
