OL,3,CElon Musk 'would like' to buy
OL,4,CLiverpool FC
OL,6,FAppearing on Times Radio, he was asked
OL,7,Foutright by Kait Borsay: "Does your
OL,8,Fson want to buy Liverpool Football
OL,9,FClub?"
OL,11,F"I can't comment on that, they'll
OL,12,Fraise the price," he said in reply,
OL,13,Fbefore adding: "Oh yes, (he has
OL,14,Fexpressed a desire), but that doesn't
OL,15,Fmean he's buying it."
OL,17,FWhen pushed further if buying the club
OL,18,Fwas 'in his son's sights', Musk added:
OL,19,F"He would like to yes, obviously.
OL,20,FAnybody would want to ` so would I."
