OL,6,FThe American investors, also own
OL,7,Fbaseball team the Boston Red Socks,
OL,8,Fand 80% of the New England Sports
OL,9,FNetwork.
OL,11,FBut, they have regularly come under
OL,12,Ffire from fans for their lack of
OL,13,Finvestment in the squad.
